      "content": "\n\nvar dia=25;\n\nvar h= 25;\nvar lockDia= 10;\nvar wall=4;\n\n\n\nvar o2 = translate([0,dia/2+wall+wall/2+lockDia/2,0],\n\trotate([0,90,0],\n\t\tcylinder({\n\t\t\t\td:lockDia,\n\t\t\t\th:wall*2+10,\n\t\t\t\tfn:100\n\t\t\t})\n\t)\n);\n\n\n\nvar o1=\nfloor(\n\tdifference(\n\t\tunion(\n\t\t\tcylinder({\n\t\t\t\t\td:dia+wall,\n\t\t\t\t\th:h,\n\t\t\t\t\tfn:100\n\t\t\t\t}),\n\t\t\ttranslate([0,dia/2+wall*2,0],\n\t\t\t\tcube([wall*2, lockDia+wall*3,h])\n\t\t\t)\n\n\t\t),\n\n\t\tcylinder({\n\t\t\t\td:dia,\n\t\t\t\th:h+10,\n\t\t\t\tfn:100\n\t\t\t}),\n\t\ttranslate([0,dia/2+wall,0],\n\t\t\tcube([1, lockDia+wall*3+10,h+10])\n\t\t),\n\t\to2\n\t)\n);\n\n\n\n\nreturn [o1];\n\n"
